{"tid":1620261,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"我彷彿聽到我老母屌鳩我係垃圾屎","createTime":"2019-10-04T09:52:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T10:05:57.000Z","uid":260380,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6fdb20d9b050bd24f6737bc2793247d63ef56676","tid":1620261,"uid":260380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:52:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「你班垃圾屎，四個月先搞到我用緊急法，進度咁慢，有損我焦土之母嘅聖名」</span><br />\n<br />\n的而且確，我地有好多手段都無用，早係雨傘時為左光環、為左（唔知邊到嘅）民意而放棄左好多手段，拋棄左勇武，所以到今時，咩手段都好，咩立場都好，<span style=\"color: gold;\">兄弟爬山，各有各做。核彈都唔割。</span><br />\n<br />\n早兩日見到呢個post但唔知點解好似無人提。<br />\n<br />\n唔敢掉嘅和理非，冷氣軍師，你地可以出一分力，整完放物資站又好、放草叢又好，畀前線嘅遠程魔法師用又得，放係屋企以防樓下有狗都得，快手整返幾排啦。<br />\n<br />\n//我的民權抗爭老將法國朋友非常好人，傳來了他怎樣製作油漆雞蛋。他說，可先用小鐵針在雞蛋上插孔以作固定，再用較輕型的手提電鑽把空鑽大，破口就非常完整，然後用針筒抽出蛋內液體（開始時不要抽得太快，否則會因蛋殼內空氣較少而破殼，亦未必需要完全抽空，視乎顏料多少，但要確保完成時蛋內要裝滿液體，方能遠投），然後注入顏料（他說亦曾有人注入混合深色顏料的流質糞便，效果據說驚人，對瓦解侵略者的士氣作用甚大)。最後，用粘性極好的膠紙封孔（所以破孔宜在靠近頂部而非頂部最尖處，因難封孔），製成品放在蛋盒內，並用橡筋捁住蛋盒，以防蛋盒在移動時彈開。朋友說，雞蛋亦可改為鴨蛋鵝蛋（但要有適合的蛋盒），威力更大，或用番茄亦有類似效果。他說，即使體能較差者，亦起碼可投擲20米遠。//<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2817389294938359&amp;id=100000019477500\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2817389294938359%26id%3D100000019477500&d=x%2FNl6Ahg6Nkeqb8F8iTJGz%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=0ed558c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2817389294938359&amp;id=100000019477500</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q58Fyv7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ58Fyv7.jpg&h=dfd91d30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PTmowhH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPTmowhH.jpg&h=c70149bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eqoVnpo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeqoVnpo.jpg&h=c6295182&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bX82MQ4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbX82MQ4.jpg&h=064d2dc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zasi4CL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzasi4CL.jpg&h=3efbef46&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4639524db0a1ce610f38c409e4777efa7bb86e63","tid":1620261,"uid":145629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:01:44.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a708f1acf084274ec54e22a5e37d870e1894d778","tid":1620261,"uid":145629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:01:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1189245874de8720a5fc0f3932300e0dee2065c5","tid":1620261,"uid":260380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:03:51.000Z","msg":"自推10連"},{"pid":"3a3a44b3331f41b1716f5233ae1e4606759b3b53","tid":1620261,"uid":260380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:04:01.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"fb9b372ed45fb310b2b883d70c1000c32dfcacd5","tid":1620261,"uid":260380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:04:18.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"2ca1964d272ae3c7436fb3f31d2d5297691385e8","tid":1620261,"uid":260380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:04:31.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"f1918f82d2d7785a196780e55ace4ee1ee21a9f3","tid":1620261,"uid":260380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:04:44.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"c94aadae049facaad6c2782ea64322677f95cd8e","tid":1620261,"uid":260380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:04:56.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"79c7584b135741c6fa9b6ce82991947f7d3e77d9","tid":1620261,"uid":260380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:05:08.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"62cca3a56680a611622084d69531253a5e9f84dd","tid":1620261,"uid":260380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:05:18.00